<template>
  <v-container fluid>
    <v-row>
      <v-col
          cols="12"
          sm="6"
      >
        <v-textarea
            label="One row"
            auto-grow
            variant="outlined"
            rows="1"
            row-height="15"
        ></v-textarea>
      </v-col>
      <v-col
          cols="12"
          sm="6"
      >
        <v-textarea
            variant="filled"
            auto-grow
            label="Two rows"
            rows="2"
            row-height="20"
        ></v-textarea>
      </v-col>
      <v-col
          cols="12"
          sm="6"
      >
        <v-textarea
            label="Three rows"
            auto-grow
            variant="outlined"
            rows="3"
            row-height="25"
            shaped
        ></v-textarea>
      </v-col>
      <v-col
          cols="12"
          sm="6"
      >
        <v-textarea
            variant="filled"
            auto-grow
            label="Four rows"
            rows="4"
            row-height="30"
            shaped
        ></v-textarea>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>
